{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1075830/extras/Story.png?t=1726515935\" /><br>Become a polymorphed deity and take back Mount Olympus in this top-down puzzle game! The Titans have escaped their eternal prisons and transformed Artemiza, a young goddess, into a gorgon. Now she must petrify enemies, solve puzzles, and dodge traps in her battle to save the realms of the gods!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1075830/extras/1.gif?t=1726515935\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1075830/extras/Features.png?t=1726515935\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Go full gorgon as a lovable protagonist brought to life with beautiful, and brand-new art that shines with charm!<br></li><li>Battle Royale with your friends as Little Medusa and the other Little Olympians in the all new multiplayer mode!<br></li><li>Customize your multiplayer battles with over 30 modifiers!<br></li><li>Petrify your way through 5 worlds of puzzles and danger!<br></li><li>Clash with centaurs, fallen heroes, and the Titans themselves!<br></li><li>Solve the puzzles fast enough and unlock a secret world, complete with a new ending to the story! <br></li><li>Carve a brand new myth with an exciting story inspired by Greek mythology!<br></li><li>For all the Greek gods and goddesses out there, we've added Olympian Mode, a hard as rock challenge with permadeath. You've got one chance to get beat each stage, defeat all the Titans, and Go Full Gorgon to unlock the final achievement!</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1075830/extras/2.gif?t=1726515935\" /><br><br>Join our Discord for discussion, news, and updates!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1075830/extras/3.g